fr fr CURSED Performance Analysis Report
vibez.spill("=== CURSED PERFORMANCE ANALYSIS SUMMARY ===")

vibez.spill("Based on benchmark results analysis:")

vibez.spill("\n1. CURRENT PERFORMANCE STATUS:")
vibez.spill("   - Zig compiler: 6-8ms per basic program")
vibez.spill("   - Cross-platform compilation: Working on all 5 targets")
vibez.spill("   - Memory profiling: Currently broken (valgrind issues)")
vibez.spill("   - Runtime testing: Mixed results, some failures")

vibez.spill("\n2. PERFORMANCE TARGETS FOR v1.0:")
vibez.spill("   - Compilation speed: <5ms for basic programs")
vibez.spill("   - Memory usage: <50MB peak for compiler")
vibez.spill("   - Runtime performance: Match Go language speeds")
vibez.spill("   - Cross-platform variance: <10% difference")

vibez.spill("\n3. TOP OPTIMIZATION PRIORITIES:")
vibez.spill("   🔧 HIGH: Fix memory leaks in unified compiler")
vibez.spill("   🔧 HIGH: Implement incremental compilation caching")
vibez.spill("   🔧 HIGH: Optimize garbage collection performance")
vibez.spill("   🔧 MED:  Add proper memory profiling tools")
vibez.spill("   🔧 MED:  Implement JIT compilation for hot paths")

vibez.spill("\n4. IMMEDIATE ACTIONS NEEDED:")
vibez.spill("   1. Fix lexer error causing performance test failures")
vibez.spill("   2. Resolve memory leaks in Zig implementation")
vibez.spill("   3. Create proper runtime performance benchmarks")
vibez.spill("   4. Set up automated regression testing")

vibez.spill("\n5. v1.0 READINESS ASSESSMENT:")
vibez.spill("   Status: ⚠️  NEEDS OPTIMIZATION WORK")
vibez.spill("   Timeline: 2-3 months to reach targets")
vibez.spill("   Confidence: Medium (core functionality works)")

vibez.spill("\n6. PERFORMANCE COMPARISON:")
vibez.spill("   - Rust compilation: Failed (build errors)")
vibez.spill("   - Zig compilation: 6-8ms (functional)")
vibez.spill("   - Memory usage: Not measurable (tooling issues)")
vibez.spill("   - Cross-platform: All targets build successfully")

vibez.spill("\n=== CONCLUSION ===")
vibez.spill("CURSED compiler shows promise with working cross-platform")
vibez.spill("compilation, but needs significant optimization work for")
vibez.spill("v1.0 production readiness. Focus on memory management")
vibez.spill("and compilation speed improvements.")
